<bibRefCitation author="Antoine, Ph." box="[465,655,1159,1186]" pageId="33" pageNumber="184" pagination="101 - 110" refId="ref22667" refString="Antoine, Ph. (1997 b) Revision des Microvalgini africains. II. Le genre Microvalgus Kraatz (Coleoptera, Cetoniidae, Valginae). Revue Francaise d`Entomologie, Nouvelle Serie, 19 (3 - 4), 101 - 110." type="journal article" year="1997">Antoine (1997b)</bibRefCitation>
